 <div class="layout-cell">
  <h2 id="id-(4.3)AgentDeskDeveloperGuide-Purpose"><span id="AgentDeskDeveloperGuide-Purpose"></span>Purpose
   <i18n-message i18nkey="clipboard.copyLink.label" attribute="description">
    <copy-clipboard class="anchor-copy-button" value="https://docs.expertflow.com/cx/4.3/agent-desk-developer-guide#id-(4.3)AgentDeskDeveloperGuide-Purpose">
     <svg role="img" aria-hidden="true" data-component="icon" class="icon icon-link copy-headline-link-icon">
      <use href="/__theme/b_8ca5a7d7-80f3-41c8-bea7-75cce14ad14f/scroll-sites-help-center-theme/41/icons.svg#link"></use>
     </svg>
    </copy-clipboard>
   </i18n-message></h2>
  <p>The purpose of this document is to describe how to build custom Agent Desk using Agent Manager integration interfaces. Agent Manager is used to manage customer-support conversations with the customers.&nbsp;</p>
  <h2 id="id-(4.3)AgentDeskDeveloperGuide-Audience"><span id="AgentDeskDeveloperGuide-Audience"></span>Audience
   <i18n-message i18nkey="clipboard.copyLink.label" attribute="description">
    <copy-clipboard class="anchor-copy-button" value="https://docs.expertflow.com/cx/4.3/agent-desk-developer-guide#id-(4.3)AgentDeskDeveloperGuide-Audience">
     <svg role="img" aria-hidden="true" data-component="icon" class="icon icon-link copy-headline-link-icon">
      <use href="/__theme/b_8ca5a7d7-80f3-41c8-bea7-75cce14ad14f/scroll-sites-help-center-theme/41/icons.svg#link"></use>
     </svg>
    </copy-clipboard>
   </i18n-message></h2>
  <p>The document is intended for developers with sound understanding of event-driven Javascript including SocketIO libraries.</p>
 </div>
 <div class="layout-cell">
  <p>
   <br>
  </p>
  <div data-component="panel" role="note" data-appearance="custom" style="--bg-color: #f9f9f9;">
   <div class="panel-content">
