   <div class="panel-content"></div>
  </div>
  <p>
   <br>
  </p>
 </div>
</div>
<h2 id="id-(4.3)AgentDeskDeveloperGuide-Usecases"><span id="AgentDeskDeveloperGuide-Usecases"></span>Use cases
 <i18n-message i18nkey="clipboard.copyLink.label" attribute="description">
  <copy-clipboard class="anchor-copy-button" value="https://docs.expertflow.com/cx/4.3/agent-desk-developer-guide#id-(4.3)AgentDeskDeveloperGuide-Usecases">
   <svg role="img" aria-hidden="true" data-component="icon" class="icon icon-link copy-headline-link-icon">
    <use href="/__theme/b_8ca5a7d7-80f3-41c8-bea7-75cce14ad14f/scroll-sites-help-center-theme/41/icons.svg#link"></use>
   </svg>
  </copy-clipboard>
 </i18n-message></h2>
<p>The use cases for custom Agent Desk are explained in detail below:</p>
<h3 id="id-(4.3)AgentDeskDeveloperGuide-1.EstablishConnectionwithAgentManager"><span id="AgentDeskDeveloperGuide-1.EstablishConnectionwithAgentManager"></span>1.&nbsp;Establish Connection with Agent Manager
 <i18n-message i18nkey="clipboard.copyLink.label" attribute="description">
  <copy-clipboard class="anchor-copy-button" value="https://docs.expertflow.com/cx/4.3/agent-desk-developer-guide#id-(4.3)AgentDeskDeveloperGuide-1.EstablishConnectionwithAgentManager">
   <svg role="img" aria-hidden="true" data-component="icon" class="icon icon-link copy-headline-link-icon">
    <use href="/__theme/b_8ca5a7d7-80f3-41c8-bea7-75cce14ad14f/scroll-sites-help-center-theme/41/icons.svg#link"></use>
   </svg>
  </copy-clipboard>
 </i18n-message></h3>
<h4 id="id-(4.3)AgentDeskDeveloperGuide-TologintoAgentManager"><span id="AgentDeskDeveloperGuide-TologintoAgentManager"></span>To login to Agent Manager
 <i18n-message i18nkey="clipboard.copyLink.label" attribute="description">
  <copy-clipboard class="anchor-copy-button" value="https://docs.expertflow.com/cx/4.3/agent-desk-developer-guide#id-(4.3)AgentDeskDeveloperGuide-TologintoAgentManager">
   <svg role="img" aria-hidden="true" data-component="icon" class="icon icon-link copy-headline-link-icon">
    <use href="/__theme/b_8ca5a7d7-80f3-41c8-bea7-75cce14ad14f/scroll-sites-help-center-theme/41/icons.svg#link"></use>
   </svg>
  </copy-clipboard>
 </i18n-message></h4>
<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;For the agent to login to the Agent Manager, it is required to:</p>
<ol>
 <li>
  <p>Initiate a post request to the agent manager as given in the <a href="https://api.expertflow.com/#25dd7bff-9418-4d7d-a4f5-fa58865741a7" data-scope="external" rel="external noreferrer">User Login API</a> in Postman. A successful response will provide the agent with the keyCloack user details.</p>
 </li>
 <li>
  <p>Make the <a href="http://socket.io/" data-scope="external" rel="external noreferrer">socket.io</a> handshaking with the agent manager as given in the code block. The FQDN contains the agent-manager address and <em>keycloak_User. </em></p>
  <ol>
   <li>
    <p>on successful creation of the connection, the socket library will receive a <em>‘connect’ </em>event</p>
   </li>
   <li>
    <p>on failure, the <em>‘</em><a href="/cx/4.3/connect_error" data-scope="internal">connect_error</a><em>’ </em>event is received with the error details</p>
    <p><strong>Note</strong>: The version of <a href="http://socket.io/" data-scope="external" rel="external noreferrer">socket.io</a>-client should be 4.4.0.</p>
   </li>
  </ol>
 </li>
</ol>
<code-snippet class="theme-code-snippet">
 <div class="theme-code-snippet-header">JavaScript</div>
 <scroll-shadow>
  <div data-component="code" data-language="javascript">
   <pre><code>import { io } from "socket.io-client"; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;let uri = {{FQDN}}; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;let origin = new URL(uri).origin; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;let path = new URL(uri).pathname; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;let socket = io(origin, { &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;path: path == "/" ? "" : path + "/socket.io", &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;auth: { &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;agent: {{keycloak_User}}, &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;fcm: "" &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;} &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;});
</code></pre>
  </div>
 </scroll-shadow>
 <copy-clipboard class="theme-code-snippet-copy">
  <svg role="img" aria-hidden="true" data-component="icon" class="icon icon-copy_content copy-icon">
   <use href="/__theme/b_8ca5a7d7-80f3-41c8-bea7-75cce14ad14f/scroll-sites-help-center-theme/41/icons.svg#copy_content"></use>
  </svg>
 </copy-clipboard>
</code-snippet>
<p>
 <br>
</p>
<div data-component="panel" role="note" data-appearance="info">
 <div class="panel-content">
  <p>After login with the agent manager, the agent will receive an event called <a href="/cx/4.3/agentpresence" data-scope="internal">‘agentPresence’</a>.&nbsp;</p>
 </div>
</div>
<h3 id="id-(4.3)AgentDeskDeveloperGuide-2.ChangeAgentStates"><span id="AgentDeskDeveloperGuide-2.ChangeAgentStates"></span>2. Change Agent States
 <i18n-message i18nkey="clipboard.copyLink.label" attribute="description">
  <copy-clipboard class="anchor-copy-button" value="https://docs.expertflow.com/cx/4.3/agent-desk-developer-guide#id-(4.3)AgentDeskDeveloperGuide-2.ChangeAgentStates">
